/// =====================================================
/// USER
/// =====================================================
/// Platform authenticated user.
///
/// IMPORTANT:
/// This is intentionally minimal for MVP.
///
/// Future expansions may include:
/// - OAuth
/// - athlete profile claiming
/// - bookings
